<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

    <%- include("../partials/head") %>

</head>

<body>

<%- include("../partials/navbar") %>

<!-- ==================================
500 Error
================================== -->

<section class="py-5">

<div class="container">

<div class="row justify-content-center">

<div class="col-lg-8 text-center">

<div class="mb-4">

<i
class="fa-solid fa-circle-exclamation text-danger"
style="font-size:100px;"></i>

</div>

<h1
class="display-1 fw-bold text-danger">

500

</h1>

<h2 class="fw-bold">

Internal Server Error

</h2>

<p class="lead text-muted">

Oops! Something went wrong on our server.

Please try again after a few moments.

</p>

<div class="mt-4">

<a
href="/"
class="btn btn-danger btn-lg me-2">

<i class="fa-solid fa-house me-2"></i>

Go Home

</a>

<button
onclick="location.reload()"
class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg">

<i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right me-2"></i>

Try Again

</button>

</div>

<hr class="my-5">

<h4 class="fw-bold">

What happened?

</h4>

<p class="text-muted">

An unexpected error occurred while processing your request.
Our technical team has been notified automatically and is
working to resolve the issue.

</p>

<div class="row mt-5">

<div class="col-md-4">

<div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">

<div class="card-body">

<i class="fa-solid fa-server fa-2x text-danger mb-3"></i>

<h5>

Server Error

</h5>

<p class="text-muted mb-0">

Temporary server problem.

</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="col-md-4">

<div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">

<div class="card-body">

<i class="fa-solid fa-rotate fa-2x text-primary mb-3"></i>

<h5>

Retry

</h5>

<p class="text-muted mb-0">

Refresh the page after a few seconds.

</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="col-md-4">

<div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">

<div class="card-body">

<i class="fa-solid fa-headset fa-2x text-success mb-3"></i>

<h5>

Support

</h5>

<p class="text-muted mb-0">

Contact us if the issue continues.

</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- ==================================
Need Help?
================================== -->

<section class="py-5 bg-light">

    <div class="container">

        <div class="row justify-content-center">

            <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">

                    Need Assistance?

                </h2>

                <p class="text-muted">

                    If this problem continues, please contact our support team.
                    Include the steps you followed before the error occurred so
                    we can investigate and resolve the issue more quickly.

                </p>

                <div class="mt-4">

                    <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="btn btn-danger me-2">

                        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope me-2"></i>

                        Contact Support

                    </a>

                    <a
                        href="/"
                        class="btn btn-outline-dark">

                        <i class="fa-solid fa-house me-2"></i>

                        Back to Home

                    </a>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<!-- ==================================
Footer
================================== -->

<%- include("../partials/footer") %>

<!-- ==================================
Scripts
================================== -->

<%- include("../partials/scripts") %>

</body>

</html>
